org.eclipse.swt.graphics.Drawable
public class ControlPanel
extends org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Composite

The control panel displayed on the right hand side of the simulation's shell. It shows the simulation time, control speed, and information about agents, places and overlays.

Author:
Miquel Martin
